Source: kanotix-keyring
Section: misc
Priority: standard
Maintainer: Stefan Lippers-Hollmann <s.l-h@gmx.de>
Build-Depends-Indep: cdbs, debhelper (>= 5.0.0)
Standards-Version: 3.6.2

Package: kanotix-keyrings
Architecture: all
Depends: gnupg (>= 1.0.6-4), debian-archive-keyring, kanotix-archive-keyring
Description: Meta package to grab all useful GnuPG keys for Kanotix
 This meta package is intended to  install all appropriate GnuPG keys for a 
 Kanotix installation.

Package: kanotix-keyring
Architecture: all
Recommends: gnupg (>= 1.0.6-4), debian-archive-keyring, kanotix-archive-keyring
Description: GnuPG keys of Kanotix Developers
 The Kanotix project wants developers to digitally sign the announcements 
 of their packages with GnuPG, to protect against forgeries. This package 
 contains keyrings of GnuPG keys of developers.

Package: kanotix-archive-keyring
Architecture: all
Recommends: gnupg (>= 1.0.6-4), debian-archive-keyring, kanotix-keyring
Description: GnuPG archive keys of the Kanotix archive
 The Kanotix project digitally signs its Release files. This package
 contains the archive keys used for that.

